Description copied from interface: SimpleFeatureExtractor
Some feature extractors will require some specific number of annotations that is greater than one. Such extractors should not implement this interface.

Specified by:
extract in interface SimpleFeatureExtractor
Parameters:
jCas - the current JCas or view of the document.
focusAnnotation - the annotation for which to collect features.
Returns:
a list of features generated by the extractor for the focus annotation.
Throws:
UnsupportedOperationException
